name: LUMI
description: Lumi - is a CTO memecoin done by the original artist https://x.com/ilya_stallone who is working in https://liquidswap.com/ and https://lumio.io/ LUMI - just an average alien from a galaxy thats... well, a little off the beaten path. By day he's grindng his 9-to-5 for a few measly galactic credits. But by night? His cramped apartment turns into mission control: crypto chats taped to the wallet, interstellar news clippings everywhere and one mtra scribbled on the wallet: "Yolo, Fomo, Lumi"
